latestIgtvVideos.title: Tribal Tradition on the occasion of Diwali at native
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
These tribal people travel to 12 villages on feet after Diwali, give their performances and surprisingly, are mute for the entire day! In case anyone speaks, they really have to eat cowdung!! Also, there are no women, men are dressed like one! Interesting isn't it?

I wanted my #first #igtv to a #special one but ended with this because of low #storage 😂 #destiny 😜

#India #Diwali #indiantradition #traditions #dance #music #art #menlikewomen #interesting #native #nativevillage #villagelife
